"2016-09-25T05:06:36.978Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":null,"comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"Hi \nThere is CSRF token fixation in Sign in with Google at https://id.getharvest.com/sessions/new\n\nThe state parameter is same for any time login\nhttps://id.getharvest.com/oauth2/callback?state=%7B%22intent%22:%22sign-in%22%7D\u0026code={code}\n\nSteps to reproduce\n1. Go to https://id.getharvest.com/sessions/new\n2. Click sign in with google, and authorise Harvest\n3. Capture the request in burp\n4. copy the authorization code link https://id.getharvest.com/oauth2/callback?state={\"intent\":\"sign-in\"}\u0026code={attackers_code}\n5. Open the link in other browser\n\nReference: https://hackerone.com/reports/55911","vulnerability_information_html":"\u003cp\u003eHi \u003cbr\u003e\nThere is CSRF token fixation in Sign in with Google at \u003ca title=\"https://id.getharvest.com/sessions/new\" href=\"/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fid.getharvest.com%2Fsessions%2Fnew\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://id.getharvest.com/sessions/new\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe state parameter is same for any time login\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca title=\"https://id.getharvest.com/oauth2/callback?state=%7B%22intent%22:%22sign-in%22%7D\u0026amp;code=%7Bcode%7D\" href=\"/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fid.getharvest.com%2Foauth2%2Fcallback%3Fstate%3D%257B%2522intent%2522%3A%2522sign-in%2522%257D%26code%3D%257Bcode%257D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://id.getharvest.com/oauth2/callback?state=%7B%22intent%22:%22sign-in%22%7D\u0026amp;code=%7Bcode%7D\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eSteps to reproduce\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGo to \u003ca